1、【Answer】：
  here is a pseudo code for linear search algorithm both recursively and iteratively, the code and comments are as follows:

  1) Iterative Linear Search Algorithm, 

    /*******************************************************************************************************
    /* 1  Iterative Linear Search Algorithm
    /* =====================================================================================================
    /* Comment:
    /* In this algorithm, we iterate through the array arr and compare each element with the value x. 
    /* If we find a match, we return the index of the element. If the element is not found, we return -1.
    /*
    ********************************************************************************************************/
    function iterativeLinearSearch(arr, x):
        n = arr.length
        for i from 0 to n-1:
            if arr[i] equals x:
                return i
        return -1


  2) Recursive Linear Search Algorithm

    /*******************************************************************************************************
    /* 2  Recursive Linear Search Algorithm
    /* =====================================================================================================
    /* Comment:
    /* In this algorithm, we use recursion to search for the element x in the array arr. 
    /* We start searching from index start, and if we find a match at index start, we return the index. 
    /* If not, we make a recursive call to continue the search at index start+1.
    /* If we reach the end of the array without finding the element, we return -1.
    ********************************************************************************************************/
    function recursiveLinearSearch(arr, x, start):
        if start >= arr.length:
            return -1
        if arr[start] equals x:
            return start
        else:
            return recursiveLinearSearch(arr, x, start+1)

  These algorithms are used to search for a specific element in an array by checking each element one by one.